    {
      "Title": "大规模监控 - 通信情报 | Mass surveillance - Communications intelligence",
      "Link": "https://dev.to/vipert/mass-surveillance-communications-intelligence-3g6g",
      "Description": "\u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e\u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e\u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e\u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__cover\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--L9dJohdF--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_420,q_auto,w_1000/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/as9i4o1xgckp4wfzcfgf.png\" width=\"1000\" class=\"crayons-article__cover__image\" alt=\"大规模监视的封面图片 - 通信情报\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/vipert\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--xwbdCRM3--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/848632/e16d7586-00a9-47ed-aa23-d5e0220891bc.png\" width=\"40\" alt=\"毒蛇T\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/header\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__main\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 你好，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 根据我的来源，这是第十三页的“预防”文件，链接在下面提到的来源中；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--zcAnXYFB--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/ut3ce8w4780rwcojihnv.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--zcAnXYFB--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/ut3ce8w4780rwcojihnv.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" width=\"298\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 现在，AI 开发人员可以评估，\u003cem\u003e图像也可以在互联网上扫描，\u003c/em\u003e根据最近拍摄的几张照片跟踪街上的人，并根据自主武器做出德国纪录片中提到的决定，那么威胁是什么？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--5wY-eA9M--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/x5rpk4z2slkdvt04mggz.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--5wY-eA9M--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/x5rpk4z2slkdvt04mggz.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 好吧，这种技术\u003cem\u003e不应该落入坏人之手\u003c/em\u003e！ 这对他们来说是一件非常好的事情，邪恶的“过于公司化”的政府，如朝鲜等，......但对我们瑞士来说也是如此！ 是的，我们开发了一个像素艺术软件，它可以将自拍转换成图像，就像数据中的光一样，比基本图像轻得多，你可以将它们存储在区块链中，同时，那些 \u0026lt;20Kb 的数据\u003cstrong\u003e限制\u003c/strong\u003e了\u003cem\u003eAI 可以用来分析\u003c/em\u003e的细节\u003cem\u003e并追踪街上的人\u003c/em\u003e！ 完整的 Web 应用程序可在\u003ca href=\"https://pixa.pics\"\u003ehttps://pixa.pics\u003c/a\u003e以开源形式免费获得。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Gw0s5VMZ--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/gy6dukjm7dz8gg048i4y.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Gw0s5VMZ--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/gy6dukjm7dz8gg048i4y.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我们正在为即将到来的 2023 年寻找赞助商，知道我们在来年应该发展什么吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Sg7LWJjI--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/7z9lov9m2dln6ahjrm9y.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Sg7LWJjI--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/7z9lov9m2dln6ahjrm9y.png\" alt=\"图片说明\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 资料来源： \u003ca href=\"https://www.vbs.admin.ch/en/ddps/organisation/administrative-units/intelligence-service.html#dokumente_und_publik\"\u003ehttps\u003c/a\u003e ://www.vbs.admin.ch/en/ddps/organisation/administrative-units/intelligence-service.html#dokumente_und_publik \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"尼科尼奥个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--xLmQakIT--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/678049/cff5f14b-9c2b-4cb5-af99-81020b476982.jpeg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"基本代码个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--WFe6rERJ--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/374182/defaf96f-5c49-4599-ba57-c2d1cbff1b6f.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"怀亚特戴夫个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--V8OkHhIQ--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/653003/87427371-5262-42c9-b2d7-76e68aae6b29.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"eyalestrin 个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--CMPYVzsG--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/497814/e481fb2b-ef93-4f00-9dab-621c5f79a66c.jpeg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/main\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"suspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 一旦被暂停，vipert 将无法发表评论或发布帖子，直到他们的暂停被解除。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 解除暂停后，vipert 将能够再次发表评论和发布帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 一旦取消发布，vipert 的所有帖子都将隐藏起来，只有他们自己可以访问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e 如果 vipert 没有被暂停，他们仍然可以从他们的仪表板重新发布他们的帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e \u003clabel\u003e笔记：\u003c/label\u003e \u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 感谢您保护 DEV 社区 👩‍💻👨‍💻 的安全。 以下是您可以用来标记 vipert 的操作：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e\u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e使 vipert 的所有帖子不那么显眼\u003c/label\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e报告其他不当行为\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eUnflagging vipert will restore default visibility to their posts.\u003c/i\u003e \u003cb\u003eUnflagning vipert 将恢复其帖子的默认可见性。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n原文: \u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e \u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e \u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e \u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__cover\"\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--L9dJohdF--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_420,q_auto,w_1000/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/as9i4o1xgckp4wfzcfgf.png\" width=\"1000\" class=\"crayons-article__cover__image\" alt=\"Cover image for Mass surveillance - Communications intelligence\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/vipert\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--xwbdCRM3--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/848632/e16d7586-00a9-47ed-aa23-d5e0220891bc.png\" width=\"40\" alt=\"ViperT\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/header\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__main\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e \u003cp\u003eHello,\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eAccording to my source which is the \"prophylax\" document at the thirteenth page which is linked in the source mentioned below;\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--zcAnXYFB--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/ut3ce8w4780rwcojihnv.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--zcAnXYFB--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/ut3ce8w4780rwcojihnv.png\" alt=\"Image description\" width=\"298\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\"COMINT is the \u003cstrong\u003einterception and analysis\u003c/strong\u003e of communications from companies or individuals transmitted via \u003cstrong\u003ecable, satellite or radio waves\u003c/strong\u003e (e.g. telephone calls, e-mails, SMS) in order to obtain useful information about economic or strategic goals. E-mails, chat messages and faxes can be \u003cstrong\u003esystematically scanned for key words\u003c/strong\u003e, while telephone calls can be analysed using \u003cstrong\u003eautomatic speech recognition\u003c/strong\u003e.\"\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eNow, AI developers can assess that \u003cem\u003eimages can also be scanned within the Internet\u003c/em\u003e to stalk individuals in the street based on a few recent photography of them and take decisions as mentioned in a German documentary based on autonomous weapons, to then what is the threat?\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--5wY-eA9M--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/x5rpk4z2slkdvt04mggz.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--5wY-eA9M--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/x5rpk4z2slkdvt04mggz.png\" alt=\"Image description\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eWell, that such technology come to \u003cem\u003ebelong in the wrong hands that should not\u003c/em\u003e! And that is a perfectly nice business to them, the evil \"too corporate\" governments such as North Korea among others, ... but that is also one for us, in Switzerland! Yay, we developed a pixel art software which can transform selfies into images as light in data, and as much lighter than basic images that you can store them inside blockchain, meanwhile, those \u0026lt;20Kb of data \u003cstrong\u003elimits the details\u003c/strong\u003e the \u003cem\u003eAI can use to analyse and track people down the street\u003c/em\u003e! The full web application is available for free in open-source at \u003ca href=\"https://pixa.pics\"\u003ehttps://pixa.pics\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Gw0s5VMZ--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/gy6dukjm7dz8gg048i4y.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Gw0s5VMZ--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/gy6dukjm7dz8gg048i4y.png\" alt=\"Image description\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eAnd we're looking for sponsors for the year 2023 to come, any idea what we should develop during this coming year?\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Sg7LWJjI--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/7z9lov9m2dln6ahjrm9y.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Sg7LWJjI--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/7z9lov9m2dln6ahjrm9y.png\" alt=\"Image description\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eSource: \u003ca href=\"https://www.vbs.admin.ch/en/ddps/organisation/administrative-units/intelligence-service.html#dokumente_und_publik\"\u003ehttps://www.vbs.admin.ch/en/ddps/organisation/administrative-units/intelligence-service.html#dokumente_und_publik\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/article\u003e \u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/nyctonio/what-is-alternative-data-complete-guide-2ln7\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"nyctonio profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--xLmQakIT--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/678049/cff5f14b-9c2b-4cb5-af99-81020b476982.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/bascodes/this-week-in-python-2php\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"bascodes profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--WFe6rERJ--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/374182/defaf96f-5c49-4599-ba57-c2d1cbff1b6f.jpg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/wyattdave/ive-just-been-hacked-by-a-power-app-1fj4\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"wyattdave profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--V8OkHhIQ--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/653003/87427371-5262-42c9-b2d7-76e68aae6b29.jpg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/aws-builders/where-is-the-osi-model-in-the-public-cloud-265\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"eyalestrin profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--CMPYVzsG--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/497814/e481fb2b-ef93-4f00-9dab-621c5f79a66c.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/section\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/main\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"suspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once suspended, vipert will not be able to comment or publish posts until their suspension is removed. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unsuspended, vipert will be able to comment and publish posts again. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unpublished, all posts by vipert will become hidden and only accessible to themselves. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e If vipert is not suspended, they can still re-publish their posts from their dashboard. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e\u003clabel\u003eNote:\u003c/label\u003e\u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\n\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Thanks for keeping DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻 safe. Here is what you can do to flag vipert: \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e \u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e Make all posts by vipert less visible \u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e vipert consistently posts content that violates DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻's code of conduct because it is harassing, offensive or spammy. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/label\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"mt-4\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e Report other inappropriate conduct \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Unflagging vipert will restore default visibility to their posts. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e",
