      "Title": "存储市场数据的 5 种方式：CSV、SQLite、Postgres、Mongo、Arctic | 5 ways to store market data: CSV, SQLite, Postgres, Mongo, Arctic",
      "Link": "https://dev.to/jungle_sven/5-ways-to-store-market-data-csv-sqlite-postgres-mongo-arctic-172c",
